I"ó<h2 id="installation">Installation</h2>
<p>Installation of the ArrowPoint-CANbus tools can be achieved simply by running the ArrowPointDiagnosticTool.exe in the following directory:</p>

<p>\ArrowWareDiagnosticTool\bin\Debug</p>

<p>or</p>

<p>\ArrowWareDiagnosticTool\bin\Run directories</p>

<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>
<p>The tool is relatively simple to use. Log in and connect to the CANbus network, typically the default settings will work fine.</p>

<p><img src="/images/canbus_settings.png" alt="CanBUS Settings" /></p>

<p>You can then access a range of tools on the menu for logging / recording or replaying CANbus traffic as well as sending and simulating data in the system.</p>

<p><img src="/images/canbus_tools.png" alt="CanBUS Tools" /></p>
